Class OperatorOnlineRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ityx.mediatrix.data.OperatorOnlineRecord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class OperatorOnlineRecord
extends Object
implements Serializable
    The class contains the period of time in which the operator was online. The time specification is defined in minutes since midnight.
